Automated Banking Website Using Agile
1. Introduction

An Automated Banking Website provides online banking services such as fund transfer, balance enquiry, and account management.

2. Objectives

To automate banking services

To reduce manual work

To provide secure transactions

3. Scope

The system supports customer login, account management, and transaction history.

4. Agile Approach

The project is developed in sprints such as authentication, account services, and transaction modules.

5. System Features

Secure login

Fund transfer

Account details view

Transaction history

6. Advantages

Secure and reliable

Faster transactions

Easy maintenance

7. Conclusion

Agile development helps in delivering a secure and efficient banking system.
